{
  "id": "adv_event_2604_02_03",
  "title": "待ってて！ブリスケ！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――それからしばらくして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 2.7800000668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "ナレーション",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "地上に戻りいつも通りの生活を送っていた四人\nしかし、雫はブリスケのことを忘れることが出来ません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.9666666667,
      "endTime": 14.3666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "みんなにお話があって集まってもらった……あのね……\n私、ブリスケを……助けに戻りたい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.5666666667,
      "endTime": 24.2565764109,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "戻るって『おさかな☆HEAVEN』に？\n私もブリスケのことは心配だけど、どうやって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.4666670482,
      "endTime": 32.9656235378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "雫の気持ちも分かる。でも、魚達の争いに人間の私達が\n首を突っ込んでも、出来ることなんて何もないと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.1666670482,
      "endTime": 43.9849890391,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "目を覚まして、雫。ブリスケは魚なのよ。なぜか人語を\n喋ってたけど私達がいつも食べてる魚と変わらないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.2000003815,
      "endTime": 54.3000005722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "でも……お魚達が傷付け合ってるのを黙って見過ごす\nことなんて出来ない。きっと話し合えば平和に――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.5000003815,
      "endTime": 63.199999999999996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "雫……ごめんなさい、私とさくらは明日も仕事で\n朝が早いからもう部屋に戻るわね、おやすみ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.4000003815,
      "endTime": 76.4964853287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃん、さくらちゃん……！　一緒にブリスケを\n助けに行こう……！　明日の夕方、海岸で待ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.7000003815,
      "endTime": 85.8298419953,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 366.66628519999733
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 633.3329535999894
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "……雫ちゃん、何か私に手伝えること、ある？\n私は雫ちゃんと一緒にブリスケを助けに行くよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.0333337148,
      "endTime": 94.257029756,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう……！　それじゃあお願いしたいことがある\n海に潜るためのウェットスーツを作って欲しい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.4666670482,
      "endTime": 103.33891169239999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.3333337148,
      "endTime": 105.3999993642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "ナレーション",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "昨晩、雫と千紗が寝る間も惜しんでチクチクと\n縫っていたウェットスーツはようやく完成しました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.3333316803,
      "endTime": 115.2933362962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "てってれ～！　『まるでサカナスーツ』完成～！\n魚魚っとさんからもらった布を使った特殊素材なんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.5000029247,
      "endTime": 125.3957623165,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "このスーツを着たらまるでお魚の見た目になれちゃうし\n海の中でも呼吸が出来ちゃう特別な仕様なの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.6000029247,
      "endTime": 133.6060118358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "凄いよ、千紗ちゃん！　魚の姿だったら人間嫌いの\n『オサカナ♦HELL』とも対話が出来るかも……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.8000029247,
      "endTime": 140.97585312540002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――その日の夕方",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.0333474477,
      "endTime": 143.4533474525,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1420.000004799988
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "一応怜ちゃんとさくらちゃんの『まるでサカナスーツ』\nも用意して机の上に置いてきたけど……来ない、よね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.3333464305,
      "endTime": 154.0394915263,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9900.000000000005
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "遅いわよ、二人とも。し、仕事が早く終わったから\n付いていってあげる。それに……ブリと言えば私でしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.2333464305,
      "endTime": 166.44953657789998,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12400.000000000005
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃん、撮影でもずーっとブリブリっ子してたんだよ\nよっぽどブリスケのことが気になってたんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.6333464305,
      "endTime": 174.2020537059,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "二人とも……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.4000130971,
      "endTime": 175.9559995492,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "ブリブリっ子の怜ちゃん見たかった、絶対可愛い……！\n二人とも来てくれて本当にありがとう。それじゃあ――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.1666797638,
      "endTime": 185.5764076232,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いざ、『おさかな☆HEAVEN』へ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.7666797638,
      "endTime": 188.6655912876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "ナレーション",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "『まるでサカナスーツ』に身を包んだ四人は、まるで魚\nの姿になりザブンザブンと夕方の海に潜って行きました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.8666797638,
      "endTime": 201.44961681360002,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1633.3349864000013
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2433.3349863999842
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3666.668319699994
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4766.668319699988
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}